<p><a name="UCC_Articles" id="UCC_Articles"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Uniform_Commercial_Code&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: UCC Articles">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">UCC Articles</span></h2>
<p>The 1952 Uniform Commercial Code was released after ten years of development, and revisions were made to the Code from 1952 to 1999.<sup id="cite_ref-ALI_0-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-ALI-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> The Uniform Commercial Code deals with the following subjects under consecutively numbered Articles:</p>
<table class="wikitable" style="left; text-align:center; margin:1em 0 1em 1em">
<tr>
<th><b>ART.</b></th>
<td><b>TITLE</b></td>
<td><b>CONTENTS</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>1</th>
<td><b>General Provisions</b></td>
